<blockquote>
 <h1 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
  <font face="Arial">
   <span style="font-weight: 400">
    <font size="5">
     American Sign Language: "divide"
    </font>
   </span>
   <br/>
  </font>
 </h1>
 <blockquote>
  <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
  <p>
   DIVIDE:  At first the left hand is stationary.  The right hand 
comes down an inch or two and contacts the left hand. Then both hands move 
downward and to the sides.
  </p>
  <p>
   <img border="0" height="292" src="/images/divide.gif" width="300"/>
  </p>
  <p>
   <img border="0" height="233" src="/images/divide1.jpg" width="285"/>
   <img border="0" height="233" src="/images/divide2.jpg" width="285"/>
